This paper deals with caching in cellular networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves distributed algorithms and game theory, which are relevant to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). Additionally, the paper discusses the complexity of the algorithms, which is related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
